'''Andrew Robert Grantshire''' (born c. 1935) is an American retired attorney from New York. He is the fourth great-grandson of [[Caroline Grantshire, Marchioness of Winchester]]. He is also the brother-in-law of mobster [[Giuseppe Angelo]] through his marriage to Giuseppe's younger sister Maria. 

==Early life and education==
Andrew was born during the peak of the Great Depression, and his family, like most citizens at the time, lived in poverty.

==Law career==
After completing law school, Grantshire began his career as a lawyer in 1960 at age 25. 

... 

Grantshire retired in 2000 at the mandate retirement age of 65.

==Personal life==
===Marriage and family===
In 1962, Grantshire married Maria Angelo, the little sister of Icardi family associate Giuseppe Angelo. They reportedly have at least one child together. 


